rpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you what distinguishes the best of you from the worst of you? The best of you are those from whom good is expected and people are safe from their evil. The worst\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43637,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/05\/abu-darda-learn-before-scholars-die\/","url_meta":{"origin":42020,"position":3},"title":"Abu Darda on Knowledge: Learn Islam before scholars die off","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 5, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Qurrah reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cLearn sacred knowledge before it is taken away, for knowledge is taken away by the disappearance of the scholars. The scholar and the student surely have the same reward. Verily, there are only two kinds of men\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26422,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/16\/abu-darda-loneliness-evil-friend\/","url_meta":{"origin":42020,"position":4},"title":"Abu Darda on Friends: Loneliness is better than an evil companion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Hibban reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cA righteous companion is better than loneliness, and loneliness is better than an ev